    "description": "《三国：寻将传》是一款不抽卡的有创新的三国战争策略游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真名将全服唯一</h2>在这里有近千余真名将，每一位名将都是全服唯一。每一位名将都是靠抓捕降服的，这里没有无脑抽卡，所有名将独一无二。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301790/extras/ad96571e9701e60c54c5a62e72d2ab68.avif?t=1749661305\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战斗即时策略</h2>在这里战斗是有指挥的，是考验技术的。兵种的克制关系运用，移动指令的实时操作，都会改变战局结果。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301790/extras/f495e903f45d52abe1a1d27dae63a9f9.avif?t=1749661305\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真谋略实时计谋</h2>在这里不仅斗勇更需要斗智，实时的计谋也能改变战局结果。即时的指挥，智略的对抗。丰富的锦囊妙计系统，多种计谋的组合使用。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301790/extras/2be58bb0b354ea5bb6fc043e4478a032.avif?t=1749661305\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >千余名城大地图</h2>在这里有庞大的真实城池体系，上千座历史实名城池，它们由县、郡、州、王、皇城五个层级组成，以供君主征服占领实施政令。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301790/extras/810b87764c348a79a6a67df6dd9c38c6.avif?t=1749661305\" width=640 height=360 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真还原尊重历史</h2>所有将领的形象设计、建筑风格设计，严格考究文献资料绘制。硬核写实，将领人物铠甲、衣着、配饰等真实还原汉末历史人文。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301790/extras/c1e45e0d6b0d6173477b968b288d0330.avif?t=1749661305\" width=640 height=360 /></span>",
